  <h3>What is Web 3?</h3>

  <p>Web 3 is a new era of internet where applications are built on blockchain. Blockchain is the technology behind cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin or Ether. </p>

  <p>The term “web 3” represents a new era of the web. In the early days of the internet, users could only access the web from a computer and the user experience was a bit more open and chaotic.</p>

  <p>The second era of the internet was when mega tech firms like Google, Amazon, and Facebook grew their influence and came to dominate the web as we know it.</p>

  <p>Web 3 represents a new era of internet, where the user is in control of all of their data and benefits from digital ownership without third party companies in the middle.</p>
